Definition: small South American shrub cultivated as a houseplant for its abundant ornamental but poisonous red or yellow cherry-sized fruit
Synonyms: winter_cherry, Madeira_winter_cherry, Solanum_pseudocapsicum, nightshade, small, South, American, shrub, cultivated, as, a, houseplant, for, its, abundant, ornamental, but, poisonous, red, or, yellow, cherry-sized, fruit
Category: noun.plant
